## Overview

South African History Online (SAHO) is a non-profit educational organization dedicated to making South African history accessible to all. We provide free, peer-reviewed historical content including articles, biographies, archives, events, and educational resources.

**Mission**: Towards a people's history
**Founded**: 2000
